{"tid":2497034,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"54歲男煙民猝死 月初打首劑科興","createTime":"2021-04-20T08:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T09:17:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d709ee04dca3790fa91b758d10b277533de68a82","tid":2497034,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:40:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/RPX4L3MWLJCIJI3A4XL4FE7V6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FRPX4L3MWLJCIJI3A4XL4FE7V6I%2F&d=aLufatioEIfsHY%2FyaDEQJ25ZeM81ILqxQ%2BPX7M1Kayg%3D&h=bd090006\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210420%2FRPX4L3MWLJCIJI3A4XL4FE7V6I%2F&h=ae2045c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210420/RPX4L3MWLJCIJI3A4XL4FE7V6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n54歲男煙民猝死 月初打首劑科興<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Gzou70Hwmd9w6IlN_TjMBYXs9Wg=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SMUAFRXODFB2PKTCBMWIEAIGJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGzou70Hwmd9w6IlN_TjMBYXs9Wg%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSMUAFRXODFB2PKTCBMWIEAIGJM.jpg&h=cdd6fab0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■死者本月2日曾在源禾路體育館接種中心注射第一劑科興。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】再多一人接種COVID-19疫苗後死亡，一名54歲男煙民前日凌晨被發現昏迷家中猝死，死前16日曾接種國產科興疫苗，衞生署指暫未有臨床證據顯示其死因由疫苗引起。本港累計有17人接種疫苗後死亡，其中15人是接種科興疫苗、兩人接種復必泰。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：盈健：溝針男訛稱首接種<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無長期病 出事前曾胸口不適<br />\n<br />\n死者是一名沒有長期病患紀錄的吸煙人士，本月18日凌晨被發現在床上不省人事，救護車送往北區醫院急症室後已心搏停止，搶救無效後離世。據了解，家屬報稱死者在送院前數天已有胸口不適等情況。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局指，死者數天前開始出現頭暈，曾於本月2日在沙田源禾路體育館社區接種中心接種第一劑科興疫苗，接種後逗留在中心觀察期間並無任何不適紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：變種襲海港城 病人行蹤欠奉  專家轟政府反應慢<br />\n<br />\n衞生署指，暫未有臨床證據顯示其死因由疫苗引起，醫管局已向死因裁判官呈報有關個案，衞生署亦會按機制，將個案交由新冠疫苗臨床事件評估專家委員會進行因果關係評估。<br />\n<br />\n另外，前日亦再多十人打針後不適送院，其中七人已出院，兩人留院觀察，一人不遵從醫生勸告自行出院。兩名留院人士分別為一名20歲男子，他於香港中文大學醫院社區疫苗接種中心打針後腦癇發作；另一人是31歲男子，於龍琛路體育館社區疫苗接種中心打針後失去知覺，兩人同樣是接種第一劑復必泰疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n截至昨日，共有741,300名市民已接種第一劑疫苗，382,200名市民已接種第二劑疫苗。"},{"pid":"817d13dd2e45a30be91adf0c0df373060a816aba","tid":2497034,"uid":8308,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:44:11.000Z","msg":"又有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n密到都唔知係舊聞定新聞"},{"pid":"7161188330031930644672b8085d4b1bc6cee58d","tid":2497034,"uid":187741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"是旦啦，唔死先報"},{"pid":"a7cefa7227113ec9a482273ec908959fdb536a40","tid":2497034,"uid":160592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:45:56.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺<br />\n科興已經超越左鬼佬野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca1d5a45c1e106d6d8e57b9bc540ef132f42e752","tid":2497034,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:46:32.000Z","msg":"連登破產果條粉腸仲有兩年就要死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f10eb51b400d8e58f2b04993ba32c984fac9555","tid":2497034,"uid":67823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:47:46.000Z","msg":"Four兄免疫能力出眾<br />\n巴基躝坦印度嗰啲打哂兩針都中肺炎 垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60de7ef5211821cb7562bf59861bafb467cdd2de","tid":2497034,"uid":369011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T08:48:02.000Z","msg":"肯定係無食早餐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.g